        <updateDate>2021-11-23T20:15:28Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Energy Resource Governance Initiative Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill establishes the Energy Resource Governance Initiative within the Department of State to promote responsible and sustainable mining practices through international collaboration.</p> <p>The initiative must seek to foster integrated and resilient supply chains, responsible critical mineral sourcing, and mineral-sector good governance. It must also seek to minimize potential adverse impacts of increasing renewable energy demand on mineral-rich countries.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
